# EmDash Standards

- EmDash uses Kysely internally but we use Drizzle for the Hono API (`apps/server`).
- After changing collections or fields (admin UI or `seed/seed.json`), run `pnpm --filter web emdash:types` with dev running, or update [apps/web/emdash-env.d.ts](apps/web/emdash-env.d.ts) by hand.
- IMAGES: Use `z.image()` for aerial photos to trigger the R2 upload pipeline.
- ADMIN: EmDash lives under `/_emdash/admin`. Do not add Astro routes that conflict with `/_emdash/*`.
